    {
      "name": "Task",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "get task(filter + sort +pagination)",
          "protocolProfileBehavior": {
            "disableBodyPruning": true
          },
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n  \"name\": \"Project Alpha\",\r\n  \"description\": \"This is a sample project\"\r\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/projects/69dde8542b75d848482182d5/tasks?status=todo&sortBy=due_date_asc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "projects",
                "69dde8542b75d848482182d5",
                "tasks"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "todo",
                  "description": "Filter by task status: todo | in_progress | done"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortBy",
                  "value": "due_date_asc",
                  "description": "Sort by due date: due_date_asc | due_date_desc"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Page number (starts at 1)",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "5",
                  "description": "Number of tasks per page",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "## Get Tasks for a Project\n\nRetrieve all tasks belonging to a specific project, with support for filtering, sorting, and pagination.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /projects/{id}/tasks`\n\n---\n\n### Path Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n| --- | --- |\n| `id` | The unique ID of the project |\n\n---\n\n### Query Parameters\n\n#### Filter\n\n| Parameter | Value | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `status` | `todo` | `in_progress` | `done` | Filter tasks by their current status |\n\n#### Sort\n\n| Parameter | Value | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `sortBy` | `due_date_asc` | Sort tasks by due date in ascending order (earliest first) |\n| `sortBy` | `due_date_desc` | Sort tasks by due date in descending order (latest first) |\n\n#### Pagination\n\n| Parameter | Type | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `page` | `integer` | Page number to retrieve (starts at 1) |\n| `limit` | `integer` | Number of tasks per page |\n\n---\n\n### Example Requests\n\n**Basic:**\n\n```\nGET /projects/{id}/tasks\n\n ```\n\n**Filter by status:**\n\n```\nGET /projects/{id}/tasks?status=todo\n\n ```\n\n**Sort by due date (descending):**\n\n```\nGET /projects/{id}/tasks?sortBy=due_date_desc\n\n ```\n\n**Paginate results:**\n\n```\nGET /projects/{id}/tasks?page=1&limit=5\n\n ```\n\n**Combined (filter + sort + paginate):**\n\n```\nGET /projects/{id}/tasks?status=todo&sortBy=due_date_desc&page=1&limit=5\n\n ```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
